data.text:
Dubai, United Arab Emirates

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 25.276987, 55.296249.

Dubai (دبي) is one of the most wonderful cities in the world and the capital city of the same name Emirate located in the northeastern part of the United Arab Emirates. It is considered one of the richest and one of the highest standard living cities in the world, famous for its landmarks and world-class facilities. Known for very low crime rates, amazing futuristic architecture, thousands of attractions, and excellent business opportunities for international investors, Dubai is located on the shores of the Persian Gulf and is a destination for those who enjoy the best quality seaside vacation. Tourists visit Dubai to enjoy the best beaches located right in the city center, near the famous Burj Al Arab, a luxury hotel with an unforgettable design resembling a sail of a ship.

Dubai is undoubtedly one of the most modern and fastest-developing cities on the planet. It is home to plenty of incredible landmarks like Burj Khalifa, the highest building in the world, Jumeira Island, the world's largest man-made island, the Mall of Dubai, where plenty of amazing entertainment options are located, the Dubai Miracle Garden, known for its incredible variety of plant species. Modern Dubai is a center of economy, business, culture, education, entertainment, tourism, and, of course, oil production. It is a transportation and commercial hub, with one of the largest airports and one of the largest ports on the planet.
